thread.title: Why You’re Unhappy (In 5 Words), Based On Your Zodiac Sign
thread.title_full: Why You’re Unhappy (In 5 Words), Based On Your Zodiac Sign

author: Kim Quindlen
title: Why You’re Unhappy (In 5 Words), Based On Your Zodiac Sign
text:
unsplash.com Aries (March 21st to April 19th) You never focus on stillness.
Taurus (April 20th to May 21st) You rely on others’ moods.
Gemini (May 22nd to June 21st) You refuse to open up.
Cancer (June 22nd to July 22nd) You obsess over small things.
Leo (July 23rd to August 22nd) Your mindset is too stuck.
Virgo (August 23rd to September 22nd) You internalize all your stress.
Libra (September 23rd to October 22nd) You don’t fight for anything.
Scorpio (October 23rd to November 22nd) You don’t listen to others.
Sagittarius (November 23rd to December 21st) You confuse ‘easygoing’ with ‘passive.’
Capricorn (December 22nd to January 20th) You try to compartmentalize everything.
Aquarius (January 21st to February 18th) You try controlling your feelings.
Pisces (February 19th to March 20th) You’re scared of any commitment.
